data.description: Welcome Home to this Beautiful 2 story 4 Bdrm 2.5 Bath home in the highly sought after Harbour Park subdivision. This home has a great floor plan with both formal living & dining rooms, Remodeled kitchen with white cabinets, quarts counter tops & stainless appliances.  The kitchen opens to the breakfast room with large island & opens to the family room. The family room has a lot of natural light, a gas fireplace, ceramic tile that looks like wood & has access to the large backyard.  The spacious Primary bdrm has plenty of room for your king sized furniture, an en-suite bath with his & her sinks, deep soaking jacuzzi tub & separate shower. The secondary bdrms are all large in size with ample closet space. The backyard has plenty of room to play & perfect for outdoor entertaining. The Harbour Park subdivision has beautiful oak lined streets and a community pool to enjoy this summer.  Located in CCISD schools. Walking distance to Ferguson Elementary. Call for your private showing today!
